## 🛠️ Stack technique

| Catégorie | Technologies |
|-----------|-------------|
| Langage | Python 3.10 |
| ETL | Pandas, Requests, PyProj |
| ML | XGBoost, Scikit-learn, SHAP |
| Dashboard | Streamlit, Plotly, Folium |
| LLM | LLaMA 3.3-70b via Groq API |
| MLOps | Docker, Git, Joblib |
| Data | ADEME Open Data (DPE) |

